title: Windows XP Corp. Edition - ISO + Serial + VirtualBox HD Image
description:
Windows XP Corp. Edition with SP2. You need a program like 7-Zip (free) or WinRAR to extract this.

XP.iso - ISO
XPSERIAL.txt - Serial
WinXP.vdi - VirtualBox HD Image (for the Vista user to enjoy XP inside VirtualBox :)

NOTE: The VirtualBox HD Image has been updated to SP3 for you.
